### getPtrAuthBlockAddressDiscriminatorIfEnabled() {#a5ecc0bb5ee3eac043a66ce779ad05747}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>std::optional&lt; uint16&#95;t &gt; AArch64Subtarget::getPtrAuthBlockAddressDiscriminatorIfEnabled (<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/function">Function</a> &amp; ParentFn) const</>}>
Compute the integer discriminator for a given <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/blockaddress">BlockAddress</a> constant, if blockaddress signing is enabled, or std::nullopt otherwise.

Blockaddress signing is controlled by the function attribute &quot;ptrauth-indirect-gotos&quot; on the parent function. Note that this assumes the discriminator is independent of the indirect goto branch site itself, i.e., it&#39;s the same for all BlockAddresses in a function.
